  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study (*) is to evaluate the progression free survival rate at 6 months,
      response rate, overall disease control rate, overall survival of BAY-43-9006 in soft tissue
      sarcoma patients.

      (*) as per Protocol Amendment No. 1 of 16 April 2007 approved by local IEC on 24 July 2007
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
